<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="288" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,150,429]" pageId="13" pageNumber="288">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,331,357]" pageId="13" pageNumber="288">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named and described in honor of Sérgio Luiz Bessa Luz, close friend, medical entomologist, and a dedicated chairman, who is largely responsible for the growth and development of the Leônidas and Maria Deane Institute, FIOCRUZ in Manaus.
</paragraph>
